Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.28,0:00:04.69,Default,1,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:15.81,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Gloucester?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:17.11,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,They're not supposed to be in Serbia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:23.46,Default,4,0000,0000,0000,,Their bulky Knightmares are no match!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.63,0:00:25.96,Default,5,0000,0000,0000,,They should have surrendered when they had the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:30.84,Default,6,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.66,Default,7,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:37.20,Default,8,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, with only one machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:47.62,Default,9,0000,0000,0000,,So this means that the creatures of Area 18 have fallen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:50.73,Default,10,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, about the mobilization effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:53.28,Default,11,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll have you accompany me in finishing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:57.49,Default,12,0000,0000,0000,,No need. Your section has been secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.31,Default,13,0000,0000,0000,,Area 11 will be difficult to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:02.54,Default,14,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:07.29,Default,15,0000,0000,0000,,I will find you, Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:10.00,Default,16,0000,0000,0000,,to avenge Clovis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:01.07,Default,18,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:02.79,Default,19,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.35,Default,20,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:10.49,Default,21,0000,0000,0000,,From the looks of it, you've already ate dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.48,Default,22,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:15.66,Default,23,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you might have been caught up in the chaos that person named Zero caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.64,Default,24,0000,0000,0000,,I called you, but I couldn't reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:21.62,Default,25,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:23.73,Default,26,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.-san came all the way here to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:25.76,Default,27,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:30.67,Default,28,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend is quite interesting, having only initials for a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:31.23,Default,29,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.51,Default,30,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... that she's your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:34.91,Default,31,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:38.50,Default,32,0000,0000,0000,,Our futures are intertwined with one another, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.85,Default,34,0000,0000,0000,,By future, do you mean marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:44.85,Default,35,0000,0000,0000,,No! No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.70,Default,36,0000,0000,0000,,So, um... she's kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:48.74,Default,37,0000,0000,0000,,I hate jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:54.53,Default,38,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm surprised at how quickly you decided, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:58.25,Default,39,0000,0000,0000,,But they say, "To each his own", so it may not be that strange, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.66,Default,40,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what are you doing C.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:02.38,Default,41,0000,0000,0000,,You're all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.64,Default,42,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you need to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.68,Default,43,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you a change of clothes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.26,Default,44,0000,0000,0000,,Nanali, I'll clean it up right away, so stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:11.98,Default,45,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we were lying before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.19,Default,46,0000,0000,0000,,A lie, a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:18.65,Default,47,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:20.99,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.12,Default,49,0000,0000,0000,,I'm C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.40,Default,50,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.14,Default,51,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.07,Default,52,0000,0000,0000,,Supposed to be dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.01,Default,53,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.77,Default,54,0000,0000,0000,,The power I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.04,Default,55,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.22,Default,56,0000,0000,0000,,Are you unsatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:36.83,Default,57,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:40.90,Default,58,0000,0000,0000,,You pushed my schedule forward a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:41.82,Default,59,0000,0000,0000,,Schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.99,Default,60,0000,0000,0000,,The plan to destroy Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:48.30,Default,61,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it would be a little while longer before I could make my move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.85,Default,62,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can destroy it with just that power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.89,Default,64,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to do this even without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.19,Default,65,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, you're an interesting person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:03.49,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do from now on? You're being pursued by the military, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.10,Default,67,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say the military, it's only a small portion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.32,Default,68,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough if I just keep a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.38,Default,69,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put up with it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.33,Default,70,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're planning on staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:14.99,Default,71,0000,0000,0000,,Men sleep on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.53,Default,72,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.87,Default,73,0000,0000,0000,,If I get caught, you'll have problems too, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.02,Default,74,0000,0000,0000,,Being together is even more dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.96,Default,75,0000,0000,0000,,If I sleep out there, I will be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.92,Default,76,0000,0000,0000,,Not at your convenience, but at mi-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.37,Default,77,0000,0000,0000,,I hate persistent people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:30.97,Default,78,0000,0000,0000,,You're being very careless about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:33.31,Default,79,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, how did you survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:34.98,Default,80,0000,0000,0000,,How is your backbone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.27,Default,81,0000,0000,0000,,And that contract you were talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.23,Default,82,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.61,Default,83,0000,0000,0000,,Fukushima, Kouchi, Hiroshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:52.63,Default,84,0000,0000,0000,,This makes it seven incidences since Zero appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:56.21,Default,85,0000,0000,0000,,After Zero appeared, other groups apparently became more hard-working.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:01.59,Default,86,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that "orange" incident, substitute supervisor Jeremiah has lost his leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.60,Default,87,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have the ability to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.72,Default,88,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, the cooperation with the police and unions are in shambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.07,Default,89,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite an inconvenience for us as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.94,Default,90,0000,0000,0000,,Lend us your strength, Toudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:15.29,Default,91,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Zero, Britannia is in a state of confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:18.90,Default,92,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time that we, the Japan Liberation Front, should make a stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:19.77,Default,93,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:24.20,Default,94,0000,0000,0000,,The information that Kyoto is giving the Crimson Brocade to Zero is not definitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:28.11,Default,95,0000,0000,0000,,If you concentrate on Zero too much, they will pull the rug out from under you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:31.13,Default,96,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, in the end, what did "orange" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.14,Default,97,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:40.09,Default,98,0000,0000,0000,,You won't answer anyone's questions at all, but you'll ask me questions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:43.21,Default,99,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to answer me, then you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.23,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.75,Default,101,0000,0000,0000,,"Orange" was just a casual remark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:49.27,Default,102,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:55.36,Default,103,0000,0000,0000,,There are those who will want it to mean something and will start to analyze it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:02.26,Default,104,0000,0000,0000,,The entire world is searching for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:05.06,Default,105,0000,0000,0000,,The entire world is moving because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:08.48,Default,106,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, is this what you wanted to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:11.73,Default,107,0000,0000,0000,,No, this disturbance is merely part of the calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:15.78,Default,108,0000,0000,0000,,The world will plunge into an even greater chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:25.14,Default,109,0000,0000,0000,,Private Kururugi Suzaku of the district 11 military, case 1075, concerning the suspicion of Prince Clovis' murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:27.63,Default,110,0000,0000,0000,,We declare you acquitted due to lack of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:30.97,Default,110,0000,0000,0000,,Why... all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:33.18,Default,111,0000,0000,0000,,Please get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.46,Default,112,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.87,Default,113,0000,0000,0000,,Um... are you injured, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:41.95,Default,114,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:43.90,Default,115,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think there would be anyone below.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.30,Default,116,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:49.76,Default,117,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that a girl would be falling from above either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:50.44,Default,118,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:52.47,Default,119,0000,0000,0000,,Is... something wrong?{CHECK TIMING ON THIS LINE KODA PLZ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.95,Default,120,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Something is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:56.47,Default,121,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:08:00.19,Default,122,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I'm being chased by bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.75,Default,123,0000,0000,0000,,So, can you please help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:08.19,Default,124,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot allow that "orange" to affect Princess Cornelia's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:12.25,Default,125,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the loyalty of us, the Purists, will be questioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.92,Default,126,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:16.09,Default,127,0000,0000,0000,,That Sir Jeremiah is wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.50,Default,128,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is "orange"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:22.60,Default,129,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, it's a fact that Sir Jeremiah is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.69,Default,130,0000,0000,0000,,Saying that he does not remember anything... it's the same excuse as Patre!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:30.71,Default,131,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Jeremiah's memories are jumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:34.36,Default,132,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same with those who had their Sutherlands stolen in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:35.78,Default,133,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:43.04,Default,134,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't introduced myself yet, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:43.91,Default,135,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:46.75,Default,135,0000,0000,0000,,Yuffie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.54,Default,136,0000,0000,0000,,Yuffie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:48.96,Default,137,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.35,Default,138,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.53,Default,139,0000,0000,0000,,You're famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:58.25,Default,140,0000,0000,0000,,The son of former Captain Kururugi, Private Kururugi Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.02,Default,141,0000,0000,0000,,It was a lie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.98,Default,142,0000,0000,0000,,The story about being chased by bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:05.44,Default,143,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.25,Default,144,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt, meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.50,Default,145,0000,0000,0000,,Meow meow meow~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.62,Default,146,0000,0000,0000,,Meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.74,Default,146,0000,0000,0000,,Meow~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.13,Default,147,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:34.83,Default,148,0000,0000,0000,,We're late, I hope he's waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.85,Default,150,0000,0000,0000,,But was he really acquitted?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.73,Default,151,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently on lack of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.93,Default,152,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like he was thoroughly investigated, thanks to that incident with Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.59,Default,153,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:46.53,Default,154,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.17,Default,155,0000,0000,0000,,Do you dislike cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.68,Default,156,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I like them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.61,Default,157,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be a one-sided love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:01.13,Default,158,0000,0000,0000,,Kind people are the ones who have one-sided loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.22,Default,160,0000,0000,0000,,It ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:06.87,Default,161,0000,0000,0000,,Yuffie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.54,Default,162,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you lie just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.98,Default,163,0000,0000,0000,,Are you concerned about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:12.63,Default,164,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.10,Default,165,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.33,Default,166,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, please come with me for a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:30.32,Default,167,0000,0000,0000,,When we're like this, it doesn't seem too different from being in Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:31.56,Default,168,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the motherland, Yuffie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.61,Default,169,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.72,Default,170,0000,0000,0000,,I was a student up until last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.69,Default,171,0000,0000,0000,,Until last week? Then, what are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.34,Default,173,0000,0000,0000,,By student, do you mean a high-schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.74,Default,174,0000,0000,0000,,You can go sightseeing whenever you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.53,Default,175,0000,0000,0000,,You ask a lot questions, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.34,Default,176,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.54,Default,177,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:57.42,Default,178,0000,0000,0000,,Um... today is my last day off, so I wanted to see what sort of place Area 11 is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.30,Default,179,0000,0000,0000,,Then it didn't have to be me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.69,Default,180,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm glad it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:03.47,Default,181,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.04,Default,182,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-san, could you take me to one more place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.15,Default,183,0000,0000,0000,,You may request anything of me, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:13.81,Default,184,0000,0000,0000,,Then to Shinjuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:20.03,Default,185,0000,0000,0000,,Please show me Shinjuku, Kururugi Suzaku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:27.74,Default,186,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:29.53,Default,186,0000,0000,0000,,Are you busy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.30,Default,187,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.02,Default,188,0000,0000,0000,,It's about that phone call from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.09,Default,189,0000,0000,0000,,Phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:38.84,Default,190,0000,0000,0000,,Um... you know, that time in the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:39.96,Default,191,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:42.55,Default,192,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know if there are call logs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:44.42,Default,193,0000,0000,0000,,I want to contact that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:47.26,Default,194,0000,0000,0000,,It's the school's phone, so I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:49.50,Default,195,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.70,Default,195,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:53.47,Default,196,0000,0000,0000,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.26,Default,197,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:57.00,Default,198,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong- whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.08,Default,199,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:06.69,Default,200,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:07.28,Default,201,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:08.97,Default,202,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.49,Default,203,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:16.05,Default,204,0000,0000,0000,,To return to the motherland like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:18.09,Default,205,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have gotten involved with that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:21.88,Default,206,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.21,Default,207,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just go wandering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.59,Default,208,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay as long as I'm within the school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:26.65,Default,209,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:30.06,Default,210,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're an outsider here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.43,Default,212,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an outsider no matter where I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.35,Default,213,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.35,Default,214,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:37.97,Default,215,0000,0000,0000,,So she's at it again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:39.02,Default,216,0000,0000,0000,,Again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:46.54,Default,217,0000,0000,0000,,I placed a Geass on her which makes her carve a symbol on this wall every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.62,Default,218,0000,0000,0000,,Geass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.85,Default,219,0000,0000,0000,,This power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.24,Default,220,0000,0000,0000,,During the contract, that's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.84,Default,221,0000,0000,0000,,A test to find out the length of duration, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.09,Default,222,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to understand the specs of your weapon, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.49,Default,223,0000,0000,0000,,If you're too uncontrollable, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:01.38,Default,224,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it would work on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:03.88,Default,225,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.67,Default,226,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are accomplices.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:09.76,Default,227,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything that would put us in a disadvantegous situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:18.10,Default,228,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinjuku ghetto is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.23,Default,229,0000,0000,0000,,People had finally begun to return, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:32.28,Default,230,0000,0000,0000,,Aw... As I thought, they won't use the RG's against Elevens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.20,Default,231,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.83,Default,232,0000,0000,0000,,It's the aftermath. Hurry up and take the picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:36.92,Default,233,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.25,Default,234,0000,0000,0000,,Take a picture of me next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:38.92,Default,235,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:41.73,Default,236,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.03,Default,237,0000,0000,0000,,The information about Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.95,Default,238,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is information from Sir Curel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.11,Default,239,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.70,Default,240,0000,0000,0000,,Put a cordon on the 4th Zone of the Shinjuku Ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.53,Default,241,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.86,Default,242,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Curel... we will leave the rest up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:14:01.65,Default,243,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to contact Sir Jeremiah, but it seems you probably won't, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.65,Default,245,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here, you Britannian pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.36,Default,246,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:10.04,Default,247,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? You're just an Eleven!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:11.94,Default,248,0000,0000,0000,,We're Japanese! Don't call us Elevens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:12.94,Default,249,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:15.32,Default,250,0000,0000,0000,,You guys lost to us, you dogs of a defeated country!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.75,Default,252,0000,0000,0000,,Why you Britannian...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.74,Default,253,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:19.62,Default,254,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resort to violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.13,Default,255,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.50,Default,256,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:26.68,Default,257,0000,0000,0000,,You... are you Kururugi Suzaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.56,Default,258,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi, the guy who killed Clovis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.03,Default,259,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.36,Default,260,0000,0000,0000,,The one who did it was Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.92,Default,261,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is just a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.78,Default,262,0000,0000,0000,,So what if he's an honored Britannian?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:37.60,Default,263,0000,0000,0000,,Acting so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:40.71,Default,264,0000,0000,0000,,Selling your pride, comrades and soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:41.93,Default,265,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even Japanese?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:43.64,Default,266,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:44.69,Default,267,0000,0000,0000,,That IS it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.61,Default,268,0000,0000,0000,,You dog of Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.07,Default,269,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:57.44,Default,270,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an individual who has received training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.30,Default,271,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight with your comrades anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:00.58,Default,272,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by comrade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.22,Default,273,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.99,Default,274,0000,0000,0000,,That traitor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.06,Default,275,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.30,Default,276,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:13.41,Default,277,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:15.87,Default,278,0000,0000,0000,,It's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.63,Default,279,0000,0000,0000,,My Prime G and MX 4 are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.50,Default,280,0000,0000,0000,,You were too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.72,Default,281,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, for being honored...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.18,Default,282,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let them go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:25.31,Default,283,0000,0000,0000,,You should have finished them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:27.87,Default,284,0000,0000,0000,,You've killed many Elevens before anyway, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.02,Default,285,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think is feeding you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:36.03,Default,286,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to insult this man any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:40.94,Default,287,0000,0000,0000,,In order to use the Geass, one must look directly into the opponents' eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.27,Default,288,0000,0000,0000,,There is no problem penetrating through glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.46,Default,289,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum distance is about 270 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:52.53,Default,290,0000,0000,0000,,After having the Geass cast on them, or when it's in effect, there is a noticeable gap in memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:57.48,Default,291,0000,0000,0000,,This is thought to be damage caused by the Geass invading the cerebrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:00.73,Default,292,0000,0000,0000,,If it has the property of light, then reflection is also possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:04.15,Default,293,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have studied it a lot in such a short amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:08.70,Default,294,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent is an empire which has subdued over a third of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.54,Default,295,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as exercising too much discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:14.07,Default,296,0000,0000,0000,,Understandable for Elevens, but you're Britannian, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:18.57,Default,298,0000,0000,0000,,Britannia is much too large and powerful of an opponent to fight with just one Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.62,Default,299,0000,0000,0000,,So everything would be okay if I were strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:25.04,Default,300,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's bad to be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:31.26,Default,301,0000,0000,0000,,At that time... for us 10 year olds, the world appeared to be a very sad place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:33.87,Default,302,0000,0000,0000,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:35.44,Default,302,0000,0000,0000,,Sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.12,Default,303,0000,0000,0000,,Corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:37.91,Default,303,0000,0000,0000,,Decay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:39.17,Default,304,0000,0000,0000,,Discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.15,Default,305,0000,0000,0000,,War and terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:43.73,Default,306,0000,0000,0000,,The repeated chain of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:46.83,Default,307,0000,0000,0000,,A foolish vicious cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:50.48,Default,308,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must break this chain asunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.28,Default,309,0000,0000,0000,,Quite an idealist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:56.45,Default,310,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I don't think that it is possible to get rid of all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.86,Default,311,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:00.08,Default,312,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:04.73,Default,313,0000,0000,0000,,I would at least like a world without war. A place where we won't lose dear ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.23,Default,314,0000,0000,0000,,Such a convenient world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:08.75,Default,315,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:10.04,Default,316,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:15.13,Default,317,0000,0000,0000,,If someone wins, the fighting will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:16.89,Default,318,0000,0000,0000,,Someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:20.35,Default,319,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:25.14,Default,320,0000,0000,0000,,But if I stop aiming for something, my father will have died in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.40,Default,321,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kururugi's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:31.14,Default,322,0000,0000,0000,,In that war, my father HAD to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:36.07,Default,323,0000,0000,0000,,Jeremiah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:40.14,Default,324,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we will make you pay for the sin of allowing the murderer of Prince Clovis to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.06,Default,325,0000,0000,0000,,Cowardly Curel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.69,Default,326,0000,0000,0000,,So the information that you found Zero was a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:48.87,Default,327,0000,0000,0000,,Before Princess Cornelia arrives, we must cleanse the shame of our fellow men!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.29,Default,328,0000,0000,0000,,Jeremiah, this is a purge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:54.91,Default,329,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:56.31,Default,330,0000,0000,0000,,Cecil-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.33,Default,331,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.17,Default,332,0000,0000,0000,,Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.18,Default,333,0000,0000,0000,,The Purists are having an internal conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.12,Default,334,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:05.64,Default,335,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and sorry about interrupting your little get together. You'll have to do it another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:06.93,Default,337,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:10.27,Default,338,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't this be a good chance to get battle data on the Lancelot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:10.96,Default,339,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:14.12,Default,340,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:16.49,Default,341,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yuffie... we must bid farewell to each other here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.82,Default,342,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:21.35,Default,343,0000,0000,0000,,If I have Lancelot, I should be able to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:22.75,Default,344,0000,0000,0000,,So!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.33,Default,345,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit... four on one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.75,Default,346,0000,0000,0000,,Cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:33.32,Default,347,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Jeremiah. We'll treat you like a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.30,Default,348,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no shame to your family name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:36.42,Default,349,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.78,Default,350,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously going to kill me, Curel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.09,Default,351,0000,0000,0000,,Be silent, "orange"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:44.07,Default,352,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think we exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.62,Default,353,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the Imperial House, is it not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:49.72,Default,354,0000,0000,0000,,All hail Britannia!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.62,Default,355,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.01,Default,356,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight amongst yourselves as Britannians!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.67,Default,357,0000,0000,0000,,That's... the honored Britannian...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.97,Default,358,0000,0000,0000,,The Collaborative Weapon, Lancelot! {bear - Not sure what you wanna call this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.36,Default,359,0000,0000,0000,,What does a special envoy want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:07.42,Default,360,0000,0000,0000,,If you are going to interfere, we'll kill you regardless of who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:08.58,Default,361,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:13.40,Default,362,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow a meaningless fight to go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:17.57,Note,363,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}MVS stands for Maser Vibration Swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.65,Default,363,0000,0000,0000,,MVS?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.57,Default,364,0000,0000,0000,,So they were already implemented...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:20.08,Default,365,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm not backing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.50,Default,366,0000,0000,0000,,Among your own allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.62,Default,367,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:32.14,Default,368,0000,0000,0000,,Kururugi Suzaku is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.56,Default,369,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can just take out "orange"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:44.94,Default,370,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Jeremiah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:46.49,Default,371,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Viletta? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.66,Default,373,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still plan on fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:55.67,Default,374,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:57.93,Default,375,0000,0000,0000,,Curel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.42,Default,376,0000,0000,0000,,So we've come to an understanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.98,Default,377,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the Chaos Bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:02.72,Default,378,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.47,Default,379,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:07.67,Default,380,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:31.98,Default,381,0000,0000,0000,,That honored Britannian...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.48,Default,382,0000,0000,0000,,Using his own body as a shield...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.02,Default,383,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides, lower your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:41.01,Default,384,0000,0000,0000,,I will command you in my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.60,Default,385,0000,0000,0000,,I-It cannot be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:47.39,Default,386,0000,0000,0000,,I am the 3rd Imperial Princess of Britannia, Euphemia le Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:48.10,Default,387,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:49.68,Default,387,0000,0000,0000,,Yuffie...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.10,Default,388,0000,0000,0000,,I will take control of this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:53.23,Default,389,0000,0000,0000,,Stand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:56.47,Default,390,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought... the Imperial Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.92,Default,391,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that, Lloyd-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:20:59.61,Default,392,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:03.30,Default,393,0000,0000,0000,,She rarely appeared to the public because she was a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.63,Default,394,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.79,Default,395,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.05,Default,396,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.37,Default,397,0000,0000,0000,,On top of me not even being aware, I have been acting extremely rude to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:18.57,Default,399,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:23.67,Default,399,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you lost your father, I have lost my older brother, Clovis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:31.22,Default,400,0000,0000,0000,,Will you lend me your strength so that others can get by without losing their loved ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.97,Default,401,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Your kind words are more than I am worthy of!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:40.77,Default,402,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it, Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.07,Default,403,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do such reckless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:44.61,Default,404,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:45.85,Default,405,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:48.78,Default,406,0000,0000,0000,,While we are here, call me Governor-General, Vice-Governor Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:52.03,Default,408,0000,0000,0000,,A distinction is needed precisely because we are true siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:53.95,Default,409,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:57.87,Default,410,0000,0000,0000,,Also, concerning the measures being taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:22:03.80,Default,411,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the preparations for the welcoming of the Imperial Princess are being readied in the government office...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:06.21,Default,413,0000,0000,0000,,You are lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:07.84,Default,414,0000,0000,0000,,You are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.29,0:22:09.72,Default,415,0000,0000,0000,,You are being sluggish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:11.45,Default,416,0000,0000,0000,,What of Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:13.39,Default,417,0000,0000,0000,,Capture the enemy of the empire's people!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:14.68,Default,418,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:15.81,Default,419,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:22.19,Default,420,0000,0000,0000,,From today on, I will be a student at Ashford Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:23.36,Default,421,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kururugi Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:25.13,Default,422,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:58.24,Preview,422,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.36,Preview,422,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:02.33,Preview,422,0000,0000,0000,,To Shirley and Rival...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:04.02,Preview,422,0000,0000,0000,,Even to Suzaku and Nanali.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.64,0:24:07.23,Preview,422,0000,0000,0000,,But... I can't go back... I can't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:11.22,Preview,422,0000,0000,0000,,If C.C. is my accomplice, then I have to use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:14.45,Preview,422,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to lie to myself any longer.
